# Note: registry.json IS committed.
# It is auto-generated by scripts/build_registry.py, but we check it in so
# the marketplace consumer can pull a single static file from the main branch
# without re-running the builder. CI verifies it is up to date on every PR
# and regenerates+commits it on every push to main.
